  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/f82e36b9d481d4d2ecc92ab69c3f6eee.avif?t=1772417109\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kurone's Feelings ～Apprentice Witch of Starfall Village～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >follows a girl who has lost her memories as she gradually develops </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >human \"feelings\" and stumbles through various mishaps while doing her best </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to assist the witch of a small village in helping the locals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/eefcb7b16e249724e41cd775aa92060a.avif?t=1772417109\" width=616 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/63229618f5896358badd5cff2cb4e2e4.avif?t=1772417109\" width=616 height=347 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/82a5b024a725b80c92e378cf17a01d03.avif?t=1772417109\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Cuteness prevails!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kurone's various misadventures will never ruin her cheer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Lots of costumes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some requests will have Kurone change her outfit, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and the nice Kurone will never refuse a person in need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Go out and explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the village and search for people in need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you help them, Kurone's fame will grow, earning her even more requests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Stats and feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kurone's progress is recorded in detail, and while she's sleeping,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you can take a peek into the villagers' thoughts about her.</p>",
